---
const zones = [
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Barrio Dalvian' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Chacras de Coria' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Vistalba' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Ciudad de Mendoza' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Luján de Cuyo' },
  { icon: 'location_on', name: 'Maipú' },
];
---

<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark" id="mendoza">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
      <span class="inline-block text-primary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-4">Presencia Local</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-8 tracking-tight">
        Especialistas en Dalvian y Gran Mendoza
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
        Entendemos el ritmo de vida de Mendoza. Por eso, nuestro servicio de sueroterapia a domicilio está diseñado para integrarse perfectamente en tu rutina sin que tengas que desplazarte.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Zone tags -->
    <div class="stagger-group flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mb-14">
      {zones.map((zone) => (
        <div class="stagger-item flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary/8 dark:bg-primary/15 border border-primary/15 text-primary text-sm font-medium hover:bg-primary/15 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" style="font-size: 16px; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 400;">{zone.icon}</span>
          {zone.name}
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
